       <div class="new_n_title">
        美19岁华裔富二代枪杀亲生父亲
       </div> 
       <div class="new_n_day"> 
        <b>时间：</b>2015-02-12&nbsp;&nbsp; 
        <b>来源：</b>钱江晚报&nbsp;&nbsp; 
        <b>点击：</b>1684&nbsp;&nbsp; 
        <a href="/e/pl/?classid=29&amp;id=281535&amp;tempid=2">查看评论(0)</a> 
        <!-- JiaThis Button BEGIN --> 
        <div class="jiathis_style" style="height:20px;width:200px;margin:0 auto;padding-top:8px;"> 
